# Bookshoes Project Overview

Book club app: React + Vite frontend, Supabase backend.

## Stack and Tooling

- **Package manager:** pnpm (required). Use `pnpm install`, never npm or yarn.
- **Node:** 22+
- **Stack:** React 18, Vite 6, TypeScript, Supabase, Zustand, MUI
- **Deploy:** GitHub Pages (basename routing)

## Path Aliases

Use these imports; avoid `../` or `@/`:

| Alias | Path |
|-------|------|
| `@components`, `@components/*` | `./src/components` |
| `@pages`, `@pages/*` | `./src/pages` |
| `@utils` | `./src/utils` |
| `@hooks` | `./src/hooks` |
| `@types` | `./src/types.ts` |
| `@lib/supabase` | `./src/supabase.ts` |

## Conventions

- Functional components, MUI
- Single Supabase client from `@lib/supabase`
- Use `Firestore*` types from `@types` (legacy naming; do not rename)
